            <h2>Welcome to My Portfolio</h2>
            <p>I’m Carlos C. Gomez, PhD, a licensed psychologist with 25 years of clinical experience in psychological assessment, intervention services, 
                counseling, and psychotherapy. I've taught at the graduate level and served in administrative roles in both clinical and academic settings. 
                I have served on the board of a midsize multinational hotel corporation through its sale to a European public company and have been 
                the president and board member of a national professional association. My skills include strategic planning.</p>
            <p> My expertise also spans research, statistical reasoning, and data science. 
                I'm training to expand into tech, seeking collaborations to leverage technology to enhance healthcare and user experiences. 
                My career is dedicated to leveraging science and practice to improve people’s lives. With my recent pivot to data science, 
                I aim to apply analytical methods to complex problems, combining my psychological knowledge with data science skills to 
                create impactful, innovative solutions.</p>
            
